Sooo, hey everyone. I'm putting this here instead of HnH because I think everyone is in this channel naturally and I wanted to make sure it had the most visibility. I started to realize that I've been unnecessarily outbursty and irritated/annoyed/a big jerk to everyone. I don't want to make excuses for it, so I'm not going to say "Well, this is why" but I do want to say that I am going to do my best to calm down, try to think before I type and just generally not be such a prick. That's not the person I want to be or how I want to treat any of you. I get that saying this won't make everyone flip a switch and think "Oh, good, DM's a cool person now" but I do hope that, over time, I earn a better status with each of you. A couple of people I was recently a jerk to that I can remember clearly enough and want to apologize specifically to: Sorry about yesterday, Angelo and sorry about earlier today, Dana. Again, no excuses, I am just sorry and going to work on it.
